&FORCE_EVAL
METHOD QS
STRESS_TENSOR NONE
&DFT
BASIS_SET_FILE_NAME BASIS_MOLOPT
BASIS_SET_FILE_NAME BASIS_ADMM
BASIS_SET_FILE_NAME BASIS_ADMM_MOLOPT
BASIS_SET_FILE_NAME BASIS_MOLOPT-HSE06
POTENTIAL_FILE_NAME GTH_POTENTIALS
&MGRID
CUTOFF 800
NGRIDS 5
&END MGRID
&QS
EPS_DEFAULT 1e-13
&END QS
&SCF
SCF_GUESS RESTART
EPS_SCF 1e-06
MAX_SCF 25
ADDED_MOS 0
CHOLESKY RESTORE
&SMEAR .FALSE.
METHOD FERMI_DIRAC
ELECTRONIC_TEMPERATURE 300
&END SMEAR
&DIAGONALIZATION .FALSE.
ALGORITHM STANDARD
&END DIAGONALIZATION
&MIXING
METHOD DIRECT_P_MIXING
ALPHA 0.4
BETA 0.5
NBUFFER 4
&END MIXING
&OUTER_SCF
EPS_SCF 1e-06
MAX_SCF 25
&END OUTER_SCF
&OT
MINIMIZER DIIS
PRECONDITIONER FULL_SINGLE_INVERSE
ENERGY_GAP 0.1
&END OT
&END SCF
&XC
&XC_FUNCTIONAL PBE
&END XC_FUNCTIONAL
&vdW_POTENTIAL
DISPERSION_FUNCTIONAL PAIR_POTENTIAL
