&END TOTAL_DIPOLE
&END PRINT
&END LOCALIZE
&PERIODIC_EFIELD
INTENSITY 0.0002
POLARISATION 0.0 0.0 1.0
DISPLACEMENT_FIELD .FALSE.
&END PERIODIC_EFIELD
&END DFT
&SUBSYS
&TOPOLOGY
COORD_FILE_FORMAT XYZ
